description: This file configures a service worker for a Qwik site, focusing on prefetching and performance optimizations.

classes.name: ServiceWorkerGlobalScope
classes.description: Type declaration for the global scope of the service worker.

methods.name: addEventListener
methods.description: Adds event listeners for service worker lifecycle events like 'install' and 'activate'.

methods.name: skipWaiting
methods.description: Instructs the service worker to activate immediately after installation.

methods.name: claim
methods.description: Claims control of all clients immediately after activation.
